            <title>[LU-12973] lustre/doc/.gitignore ignores relevant files</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-12973</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;tt&gt;lustre/doc/.gitignores&lt;/tt&gt; ignore &lt;tt&gt;/.3&lt;/tt&gt; and &lt;tt&gt;/&lt;/tt&gt;&lt;tt&gt;.7&lt;/tt&gt; man pages file because they use to be generated.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Commit &lt;tt&gt;e0db212&lt;/tt&gt; introduces man page generation from RST files.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Commit &lt;tt&gt;4943ae1&lt;/tt&gt; removed the generated part and replaced it with traditional static pages, but kept the ignore rule.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
